### GET request to generate Stream Chat token
GET http://localhost:5001/api/chat/token
Cookie: jwt=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Description: Generates a Stream Chat token for the authenticated user.
### This token is used to connect to Stream Chat SDK on the frontend.
### Requires a valid JWT token for authentication.

### Example with actual token (User 1)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/chat/token
Cookie: jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2OGVmZWM2N2Y4MjViZmQwYTg3YTYzMDYiLCJpYXQiOjE3NjA2NDQwMDQsImV4cCI6MTc2MTI0ODgwNH0.u9NpOTh59Fmjr0LFfXwIgzWzs17Jm89H4uLl3S_8llw

### Example with actual token (User 2)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/chat/token
Cookie: jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2OGYxMzU1ZTYxYmQ2N2U1ZmNlZjZlNWIiLCJpYXQiOjE3Mjk5ODQ1NzEsImV4cCI6MTczMDU4OTM3MX0.EfAZvH_zD6sxL1JKFdQM6bV3KhXeUiCx8YgA7VhZnHM

###

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
### }

### What is this token?
### - This is a Stream Chat authentication token
### - It's different from your JWT auth token
### - Use it to connect to Stream Chat SDK
### - Each user gets a unique token based on their user ID

### Common Issues:
### - 401 Unauthorized: JWT token is missing or expired
### - 500 Internal Server Error: Check STREAM_API_KEY and STREAM_API_SECRET in .env file
